There's nothing like that first couple weeks of the expansion where all the endgame raiders are all of a sudden the same as everyone else.  I say hell yes, 71 greens are better than 70 purples?  Great.  That means that the gear at the end of the expansion is gonna be really worth having.  None of that, &quot;Here's a whole expansion with a complete new set of gear you have to get that's only 5% better than the last expansions.&quot;<br />
