</div>I'm glad you said that. Puts both of our arguments in perspective :P<br />
<br />
I dunno. I just want Blizz to try again with regards to content. I'd *like* them to put as much love into the 5 mans as they did Karazhan. I'd *like* them to quit upping the ante on gear and levels with every expansion, and actually let us kick back and enjoy what we've already attained. I'd like them to NOT create another 5 raids when there are still 4 at least that will take the vast majority of the player base another year to reach. Its not quite mudflation yet, but it feels like its getting there in a hurry.</div>
